# ORACLE       VM     VIRTUAL    BOX

## creat win 7      machine

:1. **VirtualBox Install Karo**

Pehle to aapko **VirtualBox** apne computer mein install karni padegi. Yah ek free software hai jo virtual machines create karne mein madad karta hai.

- VirtualBox ko install karne ke liye, pehle uske official website par jao aur apne system ke hisaab se sahi version download karo (Windows, macOS, Linux).
- Install karo aur phir software open karo.

### 2. **Nayi Virtual Machine Create Karo**

- **VirtualBox** kholne ke baad, upar left side mein "New" button dikhega. Uspar click karo.
- Naye virtual machine ka naam do, jaise "Windows 7". Phir **Operating System** ke liye “Microsoft Windows” select karo aur version “Windows 7” ka chuno.
- "Next" button dabao.

### 3. **Memory (RAM) Allocate Karo**

- Yahan aapko apne virtual machine ke liye RAM set karni padegi. Agar aapke system mein 4GB ya 8GB RAM hai, toh **2GB (2048 MB)** RAM allocate kar do.
- Phir "Next" dabao.

### 4. **Virtual Hard Disk Create Karo**

- Ab aapko ek virtual hard disk create karni padegi jisme Windows 7 install hoga.
- “Create a virtual hard disk now” option select karo, phir "Create" button dabao.
- "VDI (VirtualBox Disk Image)" ko select karo, aur "Next" karo.
- **Dynamically allocated** ya **Fixed size** mein se dynamically allocated choose kar lo. Isme aap jitna space use karoge, utna hi lagega.
- Disk size set karne ke liye, 25-30 GB choose karo, phir "Create" dabao.

### 5. **Windows 7 ISO File Attach Karo**

- Virtual machine create hone ke baad, aapko Windows 7 ka ISO file attach karna hoga (ye file aapko alag se download karna padega).
- Virtual machine ka naam list mein dikhega, uspar click karo aur "Settings" button dabao.
- **Storage** section mein jao aur "Empty" disk par click karo. Phir right side mein CD icon dikhai dega, uspe click karke **Choose a disk file** select karo.
- Yahan se aap apna Windows 7 ISO file select kar sakte ho.

### 6. **Virtual Machine Start Karo**

- Ab sab settings sahi karne ke baad, "Start" button dabao.
- Ab aapke virtual machine mein Windows 7 ka installation process shuru ho jayega.

### 7. **Windows 7 Install Karo**

- Installation screen par "Install Now" par click karo.
- License terms accept karo aur “Custom Installation” choose karo.
- Aapko jo virtual hard disk banayi thi, usko select karo aur "Next" dabao.
- Ab installation process shuru ho jayega, jo thoda waqt lega.

### 8. **Windows 7 Setup Complete Karo**

- Jab installation complete ho jaye, to system restart hoga aur aapko apna username aur password set karne ko kahega.
- Basic settings set karne ke baad, Windows 7 aapke VirtualBox mein ready ho jayega.

### 9. **Guest Additions Install Karo (Optional)**

- VirtualBox ke features ka poora fayda lene ke liye, "Guest Additions" install karna useful hota hai. Yeh aapko better performance aur features jaise shared clipboard aur drag-and-drop enable karta hai.

Aapki Windows 7 Virtual Machine ab tayar hai! Aap ise apne normal system ke andar chala sakte ho, aur jab chahe ise stop kar sakte ho ya pause kar sakte ho.

Agar aapko koi dikkat aaye ya aur koi steps chahiye, toh aap pooch sakte ho!
